===Noun===
{{en-noun|~|s|sclerenchymata}}

# {{lb|en|botany}} A mechanical [[ground tissue]], impermeable to water, which consists of [[cell]]s having narrow [[lumen]] and thick, mineralized walls of [[lignin]]; present in stems, vascular bundles (of [[monocot]]s), seed coverings, and vein and tips of leaves.
# {{lb|en|zoology}} The hard [[calcareous]] [[deposit]] in the [[tissue]]s of the [[stony coral]]s ([[Anthozoa]]).<!--Webster 1913-->

